dct_alternative_sm: Cap Vert (Cape Verde) to Cap de Naze
dct_description_sm: From French charts to 1955 with additions to 1961.
Depths shown by soundings, green tint, and isolines; relief by form lines and spot heights.
Bar scales in Yards and Meters.
From French chart 5451 and British Admiralty chart 1001.
In green ink: "This chart corrected by DMA...NO. 26 Jun. 28 '75."
